## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

```bash
# 1. Instalar Spatie
docker exec app-agendamento-php composer require spatie/laravel-permission

# 2. Publicar config e migration do Spatie
docker exec app-agendamento-php php artisan vendor:publish --provider="Spatie\Permission\PermissionServiceProvider"

# 3. Rodar migrate:fresh + seeder
docker exec app-agendamento-php php artisan migrate:fresh --seed --force

# 4. Verificar tabelas criadas (deve listar 20+ tabelas)
docker exec app-agendamento-php php artisan tinker --execute="echo implode(', ', array_map(fn(\$t)=>array_values((array)\$t)[0], DB::select('SHOW TABLES')));"

# 5. Verificar roles/permissions do seeder
docker exec app-agendamento-php php artisan tinker --execute="
  \$u = App\Models\User::where('email','joao@email.com')->first();
  echo 'Role: ' . \$u->getRoleNames()->first() . PHP_EOL;
  echo 'Permissions: ' . \$u->getAllPermissions()->pluck('name')->implode(', ');
"
```

### Manual Verification

1. `migrate:fresh --seed` deve rodar sem erros
2. Tabelas do Spatie (`roles`, `permissions`, `model_has_roles`, `model_has_permissions`, `role_has_permissions`) devem existir
3. Frontend: verificar no DevTools que `window.__inertia_props.auth.roles` e `.permissions` chegam populados
4. Rota protegida com `role:admin` deve redirecionar usuário `cliente`
